# Subchart tarballs materialised by `helm dep update` from
# `charts/warden/Chart.lock`. CI re-fetches them on every run;
# `helm package` includes them in the release tarball. Keep the
# lockfile in git, not the tarballs.
#
# This lives at repo root (not under `charts/warden/charts/`) so
# `helm dep update`'s walk over `charts/` doesn't trip on a
# non-tgz file with `Could not verify ... for deletion: file ...
# does not appear to be a gzipped archive`.
charts/warden/charts/*.tgz
